1b:T411,Internal evidence clearly describes a non-compliant balloon catheter for airway dilation with specific technical features (hydrophilic coating, kink-resistant shaft, radiopaque markers, 5-16mm diameter range, 24-40mm balloon lengths). External tier1_manufacturer sources from Meril ENT confirm this is the Metic Airway Dilation Catheter/Balloon Dilation System designed for safe dilation of airway strictures with minimal mucosal trauma. Tier2_regulatory source confirms device safety and effectiveness. All sources align consistently. The product is a complete catheter system (not just a balloon component), properly classified under ENT/Airway Management. The malleable shaft, stylet, and direct visualization compatibility are validated design features. SKU examples show size variations consistent with described diameter/length ranges. No conflicts detected. Current title is clinically accurate and matches manufacturer nomenclature. Entity represents a cohesive product family of balloon dilation catheters offered in multiple sizes.16:["$","$L1a",null,{"product":{"product_name":"Metic Airway Dilation Catheter","product_name_display":"Metic Airway Dilation Catheter","sku_code":"BC0524A","product_family":"Metic Airway Dilation Catheter","product_family_display":"Metic Airway Dilation Catheter","slug":"metic-airway-dilation-catheter","images":[{"id":"e943ad56d92e","storage_path":"agile-ortho/products/69c3e6c239fd4a3825e631b0/cover_7985ffd8.jpg","original_filename":"cover_Metic Brochure.pdf.jpg","content_type":"image/jpeg","size":271363,"uploaded_at":"2026-03-26T05:57:16.304562+00:00","source":"brochure_extraction","width":1654,"height":2339},{"id":"820d73ef3b0b","storage_path":"agile-ortho/products/69c3e6c239fd4a3825e631b0/cover_47ca3be8.jpg","original_filename":"cover_Metic Brochure.pdf.jpg","content_type":"image/jpeg","size":271363,"uploaded_at":"2026-03-26T06:02:21.083819+00:00","source":"brochure_extraction","width":1654,"height":2339}],"status":"published","live_